      "content": "i feel like i might just be overreacting lol, i usually get bad cramps and they feel similar. i dont want to go to the er and spend all that money if it's just gas. if i take the oxy it'll probably just make me sleep through it and i'll feel better in the morning. how much oxy do u think is safe to take just to get through the night? i dont want to overdose but i really need the pain to stop so i can rest.",
